	<element name="Fell Power: Profane Lifeleech" type="Class Feature" source="Dread Necromancer" id="ID_DMSG_DADN_CLASS_FEATURE_DREAD_NECROMANCER_FELL_POWER_PROFANE_LIFELEECH">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_DREAD_NECROMANCER_FELL_POWER_PROFANE_LIFELEECH</requirements>
		<supports>Fell Power 2</supports>
		<description>
			<p>When you hit a target with your Charnel Touch, you can use a bonus action to draw some of their lifeforce into your own body. Your target takes an additional 2d6 necrotic damage and gains one level of exhaustion, while you heal a number of hitpoints equal to the damage dealt. If your target has a CR greater than your level, they are immune to the effects of this ability. Levels of exhaustion caused by this ability do not stack.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet alt="Profane Lifeleech" action="Bonus Action">
			<description>When you hit with Charnel Touch, you can deal +2d6 necrotic damage and one level of exhaustion (does not stack). You heal HP equal to the damage dealt.&#13;
			Creatures with a CR greater than {{level:dread necromancer}} are immune to this effect.</description>
		</sheet>
	</element>

	<element name="Dread Calling" type="Class Feature" source="Dread Necromancer" id="ID_DMSG_DADN_CLASS_FEATURE_DREAD_NECROMANCER_DREAD_CALLING">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_DREAD_NECROMANCER_DREAD_CALLING</requirements>
		<description>
			<p>When you reach 3rd level, your dark impulses become too great to ignore and you begin indulging in unspeakable lore that calls you down one of the following paths:
			Corpsecrafter, Fearmonger, or Plaguebearer. Your Dread Calling grants you features at 3rd level and again at 6th, 10th, and 14th levels.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet display="false" />
		<rules>
			<select type="Archetype" name="Dread Calling" supports="Dread Calling" level="3" />
		</rules>
	</element>

	<element name="Ability Score Improvement" type="Class Feature" source="Dread Necromancer" id="ID_DMSG_DADN_CLASS_FEATURE_DREAD_NECROMANCER_ABILITYSCOREIMPROVEMENT_DREAD_NECROMANCER">
